IMAPAccount lix
Host argos.lix.polytechnique.fr
User gantait
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.emacs.d/.mbsyncpass.gpg"
Port 993
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore lix-remote
Account lix

MaildirStore lix-local
Path ~/email/lixmail/
Inbox ~/email/lixmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel lix
Far :lix-remote:
Near :lix-local:
Patterns *
Create Near
Sync All
Expunge None
SyncState *
